n:left;color:var(--text);font-size:1rem;font-weight:600;gap:16px\"><span>Is it free to list my business on ParisLocal?</span><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-chevron-right faq-chevron\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"flex-shrink:0;color:var(--text-muted)\"><path d=\"m9 18 6-6-6-6\"></path></svg></button><div class=\"faq-answer\"><p style=\"padding:0 24px 20px;color:var(--text-secondary);line-height:1.7;margin:0\">Yes! Basic listings are completely free. You can add your business name, contact info, services, and serving areas at no cost. We also offer premium featured listings for businesses that want additional visibility.</p></div></div><div class=\"faq-item\"><button style=\"width:100%;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;padding:20px 24px;background:none;border:none;cursor:pointer;text-align:left;color:var(--text);font-size:1rem;font-weight:600;gap:16px\"><span>How are businesses verified?</span><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-chevron-right faq-chevron\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"flex-shrink:0;color:var(--text-muted)\"><path d=\"m9 18 6-6-6-6\"></path></svg></button><div class=\"faq-answer\"><p style=\"padding:0 24px 20px;color:var(--text-secondary);line-height:1.7;margin:0\">We verify businesses by confirming their business license, insurance, and physical location in or near Paris, Ontario. Verified businesses display a green checkmark badge on their profile. We also monitor reviews and community feedback to maintain trust.</p></div></div><div class=\"faq-item\"><button style=\"width:100%;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;padding:20px 24